## Proposed Changes

### 1. Fix CountdownWidget Infinite Loop (PRIORITY 1)

**Investigation needed:**
- Read CountdownWidget.tsx line 18 (useStore call)
- Check if selector is stable or recreated
- Verify store subscription pattern

**Likely fix:**
```tsx
// If using object selector (common cause):
// ❌ BAD
const { value, setValue } = useStore((state) => ({
  value: state.value,
  setValue: state.setValue
}));

// ✅ GOOD
const value = useStore((state) => state.value);
const setValue = useStore((state) => state.setValue);
```

### 2. Fix WeatherMap Z-Index (PRIORITY 2)

**Investigation needed:**
- Find map container element
- Check Leaflet map initialization code
- Look for hardcoded z-index values

**Likely locations:**
- Map container div
- Leaflet map options (zIndex property)
- CSS classes on map elements

**Solution:** Set map container to z-10 (or lower)

